Watchlist

Where to Watch

It's a mystery on the high seas as Scooby and the gang are attacked by ghostly buccaneers during a luxury-liner cruise through the Bermuda Triangle. The rollicking cartoon adventure includes the voice talents of Arsenio Hall and Edie McClurg. Directed by Chuck Sheetz.
